data.description: WATERFRONT ON 3 LOTS ON LAKE EUFAULA WITH A TWO STALL ENCLOSED PRIVATE DOCK!! ****New Carpet and Paint***This 3 bed and 2 bath waterfront home sitting on 3 big waterfront lots offers it all.  There are two big living rooms with plenty of room to entertain family and friends.  Step outside to your covered back porch with lake view year round.  Getting down to the lake is a breeze, just hope on the golf cart and go down the trail to your two stall private dock.  Fish year round in the enclosed dock.  The 40x40 shop is big enough to store all your lake toys.  The empy lot is big enough to have RV parking for your extra's.  Come enjoy Lake Eufaula.  Schedule your private showing today!
